<> command to move the folder to another drive:
robocopy C:\Windows\Installer D:\Windows\Installer /MOVE /e

<> create a "Junction" link for the missing folder:
mklink /J C:\Windows\Installer D:\Windows\Installer

<> Using FileZilla to transfer data
Firstly, go to ‘https://filezilla-project.org/‘ and click “Download FileZilla Client” button to download it.
https://angus.readthedocs.io/en/2014/amazon/transfer-files-between-instance.html

<> Rufus  (https://rufus.ie/)
Rufus is a small utility that helps format and create bootable USB flash drives, 
such as USB keys/pendrives, memory sticks, etc.

<> AOMEI Partition Manager
AOMEI Partition Assistant Standard is FREE disk partition management software. 
It comes with so many powerful features that allows you to completely control your hard disk 
and partitions. ... AOMEI Partition Assistant embeds sector-level data protection technology.
